    <content>What a mess is this standard implementation. The correct way to implement would be a view with parameters. That way the definition would also show up in the metadata. Is there an option to create your own wrapper OData Service that exposes this parameters as normal attributes that you can filter? That way you could fill the Attributes to the user of the app in Identity Authentication and use them as a server side filter in the CAP app.</content>
